# 公司音乐媒体分流
# Updated: 2026-05-15
#
# Usage:
# - Designed for company networks that block music/media services.
# - Default policy target: Proxy
# - Keep this list small to avoid routing unrelated ByteDance / Tencent / NetEase traffic.

# ========= 汽水音乐 / Douyin Music =========
HOST-KEYWORD,qishui,Proxy
HOST-SUFFIX,qishui.com,Proxy
HOST-SUFFIX,music.douyin.com,Proxy
HOST-SUFFIX,qishui.douyin.com,Proxy

# 汽水客户端依赖的字节系 API / 播放 / 图片域名。
# Keep these scoped to app/media hosts instead of all ByteDance domains.
HOST-SUFFIX,douyinvod.com,Proxy
HOST-SUFFIX,douyinpic.com,Proxy
HOST,api3-normal-c-lq.amemv.com,Proxy
HOST,api5-core-c-lq.amemv.com,Proxy
HOST,api5-normal-lf.amemv.com,Proxy
HOST,api5-normal-lq.amemv.com,Proxy
HOST,frontier.snssdk.com,Proxy
HOST,i.snssdk.com,Proxy
HOST,is.snssdk.com,Proxy
HOST,log.snssdk.com,Proxy
HOST,mon.snssdk.com,Proxy

